---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Meet The Savvy Granny — sharing budget-friendly recipes and smart kitchen finds so you can eat well and spend less."
>
  <article class="container page">
    <span class="eyebrow">Nice to meet you</span>
    <h1>About The Savvy Granny</h1>
    <p>
      Welcome to my kitchen! I'm the Savvy Granny, and I believe good food should never
      cost a fortune. After decades of feeding family on a budget, I've learned that the
      tastiest meals are often the thriftiest ones.
    </p>
    <p>
      On this site I share <strong>budget-friendly recipes</strong> that are simple,
      wholesome, and easy on the wallet — plus the affordable kitchen tools and pantry
      staples I genuinely use and love. Every recipe includes a rough cost so you always
      know what you're getting into.
    </p>
    <p>
      Some of the product links on this site are affiliate links, which means I may earn
      a small commission if you buy through them — at no extra cost to you. It's what
      keeps the recipes free. You can read the full
      <a href="/disclosure">affiliate disclosure here</a>.
    </p>
    <p class="muted"><em>This is placeholder text — tell me your real story and I'll write this page properly for you.</em></p>
    <p><a class="btn" href="/recipes">Start with the recipes →</a></p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page { max-width: 720px; padding: 2.5rem 1.25rem 2rem; }
  .page h1 { font-size: 2.3rem; margin: 0.3rem 0 1rem; }
  .page p { font-size: 1.08rem; }
</style>
